# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if lock file should not be tracked, uncomment the next line:
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipenv, poetry.lock is generally recommended to be tracked in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if lock file should not be tracked, uncomment the next line:
#poetry.lock

